# 🚂 Railway.app Configuration

## railway.json - Railway Service Definition

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://railway.app/railway.schema.json",
  "name": "Gang Indo Bot",
  "description": "Premium Indonesian Discord Bot - 24/7 Online",
  "services": {
    "api": {
      "image": "node:18-alpine",
      "build": {
        "command": "npm install && npm run build"
      },
      "start": "npm start",
      "port": 3000,
      "domain": true,
      "environment": {
        "NODE_ENV": "production",
        "PORT": "3000"
      },
      "volumes": [
        {
          "path": "/app/dist",
          "type": "ephemeral"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "plugins": {
    "postgres": {
      "type": "postgres",
      "version": "15"
    }
  }
}
```

## Cara Setup:

1. **Create Railway Account**: https://railway.app
2. **Connect GitHub**: Authorize Railway dengan GitHub
3. **Deploy from GitHub**:
   - Select repo: `PembuatWebIndonesia/Gang-indo-botwkw`
   - Select branch: `setup/24-7-production`
4. **Add Environment Variables**:
   ```
   DISCORD_TOKEN=your_token
   DISCORD_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id
   DISCORD_GUILD_ID=your_guild_id
   ```
5. **Deploy**: Railway auto-detects Node.js dan auto-deploy!

## Railway Benefits vs Render:

✅ **NO auto-sleep** - Always 24/7 online  
✅ **1GB RAM** vs Render 512MB  
✅ **$5/month free** includes database  
✅ **Instant deploys** - ~30 detik  
✅ **Better support** - Discord community  
✅ **No Keep-Alive needed** 🎉

---

**Rekomendasi**: Gunakan Railway! 🚂
